\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Our modified Willshaw network which models the Mushroom Body circuit. The inputs ($KC_{in}$ / $N_b$) represent the aggregate input to each KC (the sum of all linked vPNs). The output represents the output of the EN. \relax }}{13}
